297
00:16:04,450 --> 00:16:06,870
I'm doing this for you, little buddy.
我可是为了你才做的 小伙计

298
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:15,780
Okay, we don't have that in stock...
我们现在没有存货...

299
00:16:16,590 --> 00:16:19,620
