an allergic reaction to peanuts.
对不起 我朋友对花生过敏了

311
00:16:52,460 --> 00:16:54,580
- No, he's not.
- Yes, he is.
- 不 他没有
- 他真的过敏了

312
00:16:54,590 --> 00:16:57,250
Look, sir, we are very
busy here, and I...
先生 我们很忙 我...

313
00:16:57,260 --> 00:17:00,220
holy crap!
我的妈呀!

314
00:17:00,600 --> 00:17:02,940
Please help me!
请救救我!

315
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:06,020
Code four! I need a gurney!
急救! 这里需要担架!

316
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:08,410
- Right away! Right away!
- Thank you.
- 在这里 在这里
- 谢谢你

317
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:14,890
Say what you will about the
healthcare system in this country,
虽然你对医疗体系充满期待

318
00:17:14,910 --> 00:17:18,770
but when they're afraid
of lawsuits, *********
可他们怕吃官司
还是会做系统的检查

319
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:22,860
I really don't think the
colonoscopy was necessary.
结肠镜检查真没必要

320
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:26,460
You know, before you got all swollen up,
要知道 在你肿起来之前

321
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:28,940
I actually thought you were trying
to keep me out of the apartment
我以为你要骗我出公寓

322
00:17:28,950 --> 00:17:31,640
so you could throw me a surprise party.
好为我开一个惊喜派对

323
00:17:31,650 --> 00:17:33,560
