birthday. I completely forgot.
我不知道是你生日 我完全忘记了

325
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:39,410
Wow, what a lousy way to spend a
birthday. Well, it's all over now.
这个生日过得太糟了 现在全都完了

326
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:45,590
There is a party, isn't there?
确实有派对 是吗?

327
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,360
Maybe.
可能吧

328
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:49,790
Howard?
Howard?

329
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:51,030
Are you mad?
你生气了?

330
00:17:51,050 --> 00:17:53,220
How could I be mad?
我怎么会生气呢?

331
00:17:53,230 --> 00:17:58,060
You actually risked your life
because you care about me.
你可是冒了生命危险
因为你关心我

332
00:17:58,070 --> 00:18:00,660
Yeah, that's why I did it.
对 所以我才这么做的

333
00:18:03,060 --> 00:18:06,610
All right. Here we go.
好的 咱们瞧瞧

334
00:18:06,940 --> 00:18:09,860
