快看 Leonard 我在你的生日派对上

340
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:39,850
I don't know where you are,
dude, but it's really kick-ass!
我不知道你在哪儿 哥们儿
这个派对棒呆了!

341
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:42,800
Everyone is very, very drunk and...
每个人都喝得很醉很醉 而且...

342
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:48,270
oh, and look, there's a
girl taking her shirt off!
快看 那个女孩把上衣脱了!

343
00:18:49,490 --> 00:18:51,400
That's my friend carol.
她是我朋友Carol

344
00:18:51,410 --> 00:18:54,140
Remind me-- I gotta
introduce her to howard.
差点忘了 我要把她介绍给Howard

345
00:18:54,870 --> 00:18:58,750
Oh, sweet krishna,
shake that rupee maker!
亲爱的克利须那神啊!
快摇起你那宝贝来!

346
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:02,670
I'm so sorry you didn't get your party.
对不起 你没赶上自己的派对

